  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the katsuramuki-cut carrots and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned on both sides, about 5-6 minutes per side.",
    "Add the coconut flakes and smoked paprika, stir to combine.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the skillet and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cover with a lotus leaf wrap, cooking for an additional 10-12 minutes.",
    "Remove the skillet from heat and let rest for 2-3 minutes before serving."
